Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:47.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for offering to clean Shin'ichi's house, Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:51.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem! We have nothing to do anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:53.09,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}"We"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.82,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't decide these things on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:59.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But it {\i1}will{\i0} turn into a ghost house if we don't clean it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:00.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:07.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi must be happy to have such a thoughtful girlfriend as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:09.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:11.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.14,0:02:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.84,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're off, Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You'll pay for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:31.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not thinking of cleaning the entire house, are you, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's do as much as we can for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:39.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Does that mean we're going to clean all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:41.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:44.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:53.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did Sonoko-{\i1}sama{\i0} get stuck cleaning Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s house
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:55.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on such a nice Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:59.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've just ignored it, yet you went and got Doc's spare key!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just figured the place was covered in dust
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:06.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and that it'd be hard to clean alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.09,0:03:08.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:14.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sonoko. You should dust the bookcases before sweeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:18.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like they say, you should clean from the top down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.57,0:03:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you're supposed to follow the tiles when sweeping the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like such an old hag...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls these days are supposed to be crazy about catching men
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:34.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and experiencing pure love, first love, and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:37.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet here I am, getting covered in dust for that mystery dweeb...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm oh-so-pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:44.00,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So sorry for the trouble, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:47.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Speaking of first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you suppose Shin'ichi's first love was like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:58.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've had a love or two by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:03.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. He's super-dull in the head when it comes to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, given his hot mother, it was probably a TV idol, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you've always been together since you were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:20.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, you're thoughtful {\i1}and{\i0} strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:24.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows, maybe {\i1}you're{\i0} his first love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:24.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:32.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! We only played together when we were kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:35.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then there's your precedent, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0} your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Don't make stuff up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:49.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Your bashfulness says otherwise, Girl of Twenty Faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:52.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off, Sonoko! Before I get mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.87,0:04:55.53,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Who could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.14,0:05:00.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dumb! It's obviously Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No, I kind of doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he ring the doorbell to his own house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably heard about us from the doc and wants to surprise us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.11,0:05:11.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's {\i1}not{\i0} me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.35,0:05:14.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Shin'ichi didn't say anything about coming home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:19.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you so embarrassed about? Hurry and see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:21.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's your first love prince, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:25.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:27.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:29.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.61,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Huh?! Isn't she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:38.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, are you Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.24,0:05:41.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She was student body president during our first year of middle school!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:48.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! Asami Uchida-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:49.93,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,320)}Asami Uchida (18)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 1st Year
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:55.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. So Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0} has been away for a while on some cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:58.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why I always got the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, it's almost like I've asked you to clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:05.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no problem at all! I had nothing else to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}. Why did you want to see Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:14.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends in the university's mystery club are going to rent a lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:17.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and hold a birthday party for me this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:21.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to invite Kudo-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:27.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing as he's a great detective and an old soccer club teammate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:30.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I sent the letter quite a while back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.90,0:06:34.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything before he left home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.43,0:06:37.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh no! I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I was sure he would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he forgot about that confession four years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:48.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:51.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I guess I can't blame him for forgetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:57.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First loves are bound to fade away with time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,F-First love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:00.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:08.17,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}She was Shin'ichi's first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.17,0:07:12.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it. It all makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was talking about it our first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:18.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly a first-year boy made a pass at Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.24,0:07:21.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that daredevil was actually Shin'ichi Kudo, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:25.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't like that. It was an actual confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Uh oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:29.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:31.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, say!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.69,0:07:35.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Shin'ichi-{\i1}niichan{\i0} won't go, why not ask someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:39.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:43.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've solved a few cases ourselves, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:45.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:50.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We might be able to catch some lively Tohto boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:55.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I think my male friends would love having high school girls attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.15,0:07:59.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, if you invite us, there's no question that he'll come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:00.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sonoko! You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:07.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! The great detective who needs no introduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A get-together of Tohto University's mystery study club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:14.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.20,0:08:17.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't allow you to go to a sleepover without any real adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:19.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're invited too, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:24.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy! I don't have time to mess with stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As a great detective, you can't relax on a weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:40.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But for the mystery study club, Kogoro Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0} is almost like a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:44.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How they'd all like to hear from the peerless detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:47.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention all the pretty girls who'll be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,including Asami Uchida-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, who holds the title of Miss Tohto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Tohto?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.04,0:08:58.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're busy, we'll accept that we can't go either...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:03.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure I can somehow rearrange my busy schedule
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:06.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to go with you as your chaperone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:11.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I wouldn't want to disappoint all the promising youngsters
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of this mystery study club!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:19.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If my stories about the cases I've solved can help them in any way,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it may be my duty as a great detective to assist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What a predictable personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.94,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Miss Tohto...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! We're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:44.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is the lodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:45.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:50.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bus stop is here, so we go up and right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:52.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:57.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Over there? Miss Tohto isn't too far now! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm gonna get me a Tohto boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.44,0:10:08.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...being able to talk and drink with the young minds of Tohto U!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, you're all good-looking boys and pretty girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:19.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:25.29,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,290)}Manabu Sawai (22)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 4th Year\NPresident of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:21.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I'd expect from a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:25.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how to control people's hearts with words alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:31.00,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(406,290)}Tomoko Hayasaka (21)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 4th Year\NV.P. of Mystery Study Club
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Are you sure you're not referring to yourself, playboy Sawai-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made a 1st-year girl cry just recently, President!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:37.67,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(180,320)\fs22}Chika Miyazaki (19)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:37.67,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(460,320)\fs22}Shibahisa Noguchi (20)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 2nd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:38.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:42.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! This is Asami's birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.11,0:10:43.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the time to put me on trial!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And it's also a celebration party
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:51.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for the "Newcomer Award" her novel won the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was too bad, Morimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:55.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you made it to the final selection, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:01.57,Character Card,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,320)}Yoshinobu Morimoto (22)\NTohto Univ. Literature Dept., 3rd Year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:11:02.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to Asami-{\i1}kun{\i0}, our department's most promising writer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.03,0:11:03.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of losing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to her pair in the Literature Department's tennis tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus she was named Miss Tohto as a freshman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:14.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even make it through the preliminary round...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:19.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really admire her. She can do everything, but doesn't act conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's also an incredible cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.62,0:11:24.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, where is her lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.79,0:11:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She and Ran are baking it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:30.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Asami-{\i1}kun{\i0} said she was going to make one and bring it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:32.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I've been looking forward to this!\N- Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sloppy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really make this, Asami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did. It was my first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your pie, Asami-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:49.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I accidentally forgot to bring it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:54.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would make one for me, so I asked her to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:57.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez. Why're you making stuff you don't know how to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:11:59.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:02.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Save your criticism until after you've tried it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? This pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little fragrant, but it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:14.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:16.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Me too!\N- Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.78,0:12:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is! This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:29.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It looks iffy, but tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:34.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:37.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? With cooking, substance is what matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:41.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you eat it, you can't tell what it looks like anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:52.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've solved every case 100% of the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.51,0:12:54.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you solved the case?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:55.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:59.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I was the one who solved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:02.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! What a pretty cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:05.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I went all the way to Ginza to get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find some matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's okay. I borrowed Sawai-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s lighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:20.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At any age, watching birthday candles being lit is so exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.37,0:13:22.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, only until you're 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.84,0:13:25.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Once you're over 20, you start to hate each extra candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:41.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Congratulations.\NI pray for even greater future success.\NTohto Literature Prof. Masao Takamura"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:40.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.83,0:13:44.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right at midnight, as promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:47.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's good we got a lodge with a fax machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takamura-{\i1}sensei{\i0} sent it, Asami!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.90,0:13:54.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.91,0:13:57.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. What should we do with the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:14:00.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't we supposed to go to the karaoke place by the station next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.88,0:14:03.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I already made reservations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:04.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's save the cake for tomorrow and go do karaoke ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:13.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Nothing else we can do. Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.81,0:14:23.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}"Karaoke Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:23.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}ahh  nazo ga tokete-yuku\N{\blur0\c\3c}Ahh, the mystery begins to unravel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:28.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}nazo ga tokete-yuku...\N{\blur0\c\3c}The mystery begins to unravel
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, little boy. Want to sing Two-Mix with me next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:35.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I'll go next!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}negaigoto hitotsu-dake kanaete-kureru-nara\N{\blur0\c\3c}If I could have one wish granted
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:54.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kizutsukeatta ai ga hajimaranai-you ni...\N{\blur0\c\3c}It would be that our love wouldn't make us both hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.03,0:14:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the glum look?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing! I'm not glum at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.71,0:14:51.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I guess what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:53.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart and beautiful, a sports warrior and scholar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:59.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Considerate, popular, and #1 at everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! How could you tell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}doushite futari wa deatta no?\N{\blur0\c\3c}How did they meet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:26.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}kon'na ni sabishii yuuhi o miru nante\N{\blur0\c\3c}Looking at such a lonely sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:34.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}ki no ki'ita kotoba sagashite mo\N{\blur0\c\3c}Even as I try to find clever words
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\a7\fs22\blur2\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&}hanareta kokoro o tsunagu kotoba nakute\N{\blur0\c\3c}There are none to connect our distant hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.26,0:15:08.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm no match for her!" is written all over your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:12.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't blame Shin'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0} for falling for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She {\i1}was{\i0} the soccer club's manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry about it! She must've rejected him anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:26.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.42,0:15:31.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know Shin'ichi loves lemon pie, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.92,0:15:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it for the first time today from Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:40.56,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Eh? Shin'ichi loves lemon pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:43.20,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Yes! It's his favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.20,0:15:47.57,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I told everyone I'd make one because I thought he'd come today,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:49.04,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}so I brought this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.94,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh? Shin'ichi does?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.64,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He loves this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.64,0:15:59.82,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur2}I can teach you how to make it if you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.82,0:16:03.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She knows so much about Shin'ichi that I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.76,0:16:09.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:17.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, cheer up! You have your own good qualities too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.90,0:16:19.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:24.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know! You {\i1}are{\i0} strong and brawny\N'cause you practice karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.34,0:16:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.61,0:16:35.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? There are a lot fewer people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you were taking so long in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ran off to the bathrooms by the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you have my cigarettes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:48.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some at the convenience store next door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.53,0:16:50.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Noguchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:56.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still walking around the train station to sober up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already past 3:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should head back. We left the place messy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's tidy up and hit the hay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Is that a fire?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:11.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold on! Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:15.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...our lodge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0} is still in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:28.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to the lodge!\NWe might still make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the rental car key?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:31.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noguchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} has it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:38.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"What's the problem"?!\NThe lodge we rented is on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\i1}Sempai{\i0}... {\i1}Sempai{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.36,0:17:52.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Please be all right, Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:02.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:05.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Asami!\N- Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:08.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! It doesn't look like she fled outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:11.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't tell me she's still asleep inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:12.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:16.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we call her on the phone?! She was asleep in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! It's already burned up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.69,0:18:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's no use! There's no way inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:29.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:30.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous! Step back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.43,0:18:37.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Move that motorcycle!\NWe don't want its gasoline to ignite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.07,0:18:37.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.71,0:18:40.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the fire truck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:44.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? My helmet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:47.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm coming, {\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Ran and Conan went inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,President Sawai followed them, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:08.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sempai{\i0}! Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:09.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:11.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, Mouri-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:14.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! My daughter's in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be in danger too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran. Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:32.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.13,0:19:36.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:38.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.84,0:19:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A hospital near the lodge.\NThey brought you here afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:50.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Asami-{\i1}sempai{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleeping right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:58.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Other than a little carbon monoxide poisoning, she's just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness! She made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:05.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about? You're the one who saved her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:12.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing at all... I rushed inside without thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:17.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sawai-{\i1}san{\i0} led the way to safety after I found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:22.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt relieved when I got outside,\Nbut things got blurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:26.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was amazing! You busted inside with that helmet on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.05,0:20:30.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the firefighters said that it wasn't smart to go into the fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:33.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but wearing the helmet was the correct thing to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.39,0:20:36.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that was Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:41.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave it to me just as I was about to run inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:46.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said I should put it on to protect my hair and face from the flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:50.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0} did? He's as strange a kid as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:53.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:03.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So the fire started around 2:50?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. People in nearby lodges\Nsaid they saw smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:12.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They thought it was a bonfire at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:15.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you suspect it was arson?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:18.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The fire started in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:21.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This cake candle was probably the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cake candle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.11,0:21:28.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It probably fell onto the floor while still lit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:33.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where it ignited the nearby wrapping paper and curtains.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you blow them out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:38.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I did put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:42.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped. We were all in a hurry when we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I put them out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.96,0:21:48.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the candle did burn down to its base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.16,0:21:54.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't forget to put it out, there's one other possibility...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:22:00.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The possibility that Asami-{\i1}san{\i0} herself lit the fire in the living room!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:01.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.28,0:22:03.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd! Why would she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:24:08.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(120,104)\fnSegoe\fscx105\fs28\fsp1\shad0\bord0\alpha&H1F&}NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:48.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}S-Sempai{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.65,0:23:50.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.25,0:23:53.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must've left while we were getting something to drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:55.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Asami-{\i1}san{\i0} was nearly burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:08.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By one of you here!
