Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.43,0:24:20.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.26,0:24:22.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm gonna close in on the truth of his first love!
